headline: E.l.f. Beauty CEO rejects growth fears, points to 'great momentum' following Hailey Bieber deal
summary: From 14-hour lines for Rhode to dominance at Dollar General, e.l.f. Beauty says its "pipeline" is stronger than analysts think.
